Documentation is like sex:
When it's good, it's very good.
When it's bad, it's better than nothing...

data.joke_1: Programming is 10% science, 20% ingenuity, and 70% getting the ingenuity to work with the science.

data.joke_2: My ex had an accident. I told the paramedics the wrong blood type for her. She'll finally experience what rejection is really like.

data.joke_3:
Hey Girl,
Roses are #ff0000,
Violets are #0000ff,
I use hex codes,
But I'd use RGB for you.
